{"tid":1437282,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人對美國有認識 我屋企人send咗段片俾我 想駁嘴","createTime":"2019-08-09T13:21:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T17:54:12.000Z","uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"64d25f0df81e2069b90b48b6a85dc0840e925da2","tid":1437282,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:21:01.000Z","msg":"是咁的 我屋企人send咗條片俾我<br />\n<br />\n內容大概就係話美國民主兩個字隔離仲有法治<br />\n喺美國有衝突都會俾警察拉 而且比香港警察更高武力<br />\n所以美國唔係想像中咁好 遇到同樣事都會暴力清場 咁<br />\n<br />\n我就想反駁翻佢內容 可惜我才疏學淺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時香港嘢都答到 可以講民主重要性/警黑<br />\n但我對美史同美國政況真係冇乜認識<br />\n希望有連登才子幫幫手<br />\n講下段片邊個位有問題 或者美國係點<br />\n有論點論證俾我send翻俾佢等佢駁唔到<br />\n我知呢啲係俾藍 親中睇<br />\n但希望大家救下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等我屋企人個腦hang機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁我聽少幾日説話<br />\n大家又可以學下駁嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔洗慳負皮 我自己俾一個自己先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0197ca8f1021bfb209cf706be9485cf303dcf1f","tid":1437282,"uid":12628,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:22:53.000Z","msg":"美國有三權分立嘅政體保護國民，告政府係成日都有嘅事，香港呢？三權配合政權"},{"pid":"f47881aba0d36aff9a1a1cdc3e4fc1b12de15ae3","tid":1437282,"uid":7391,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:23:37.000Z","msg":"香港而家係人治唔係法治"},{"pid":"f1eeef6e0b291c411a71ed1b719009292a50f18e","tid":1437282,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:24:03.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"57c6da58c5bde257eeae0791e1c8874b2ffaaf52","tid":1437282,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:25:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af8fbb6704a1d13eaa0f18890d213b10f32e30f8","tid